WEBVTT

00:02:58.680 --> 00:03:01.056
that are identified as in poverty.

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:04.696
The children had very little experience
of being outside in the countryside,

00:03:04.720 --> 00:03:06.736
knowing about food-growing.

00:03:06.760 --> 00:03:08.336
Over a period of time,

00:03:08.360 --> 00:03:09.880
we were able to build a garden.

00:03:10.520 --> 00:03:12.640
(Children shout)

00:03:13.880 --> 00:03:16.656
Students: Welcome to the Secret Garden!

00:03:16.680 --> 00:03:18.256
Kehinde: This is our greenhouse.

00:03:18.280 --> 00:03:19.536
This is our compost bin.

00:03:19.560 --> 00:03:21.016
This is our wormery.

00:03:21.040 --> 00:03:23.560
(Music)

00:03:25.080 --> 00:03:26.760
This is our vegetable patch.

00:03:29.560 --> 00:03:31.000
And these are our chickens.